N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4820.34 - Persons prohibited as player

State Regulations

No licensee shall permit any person who has participated
or assisted in the management or conduct of the bingo occasion to participate
as a bingo player or purchase bell jar tickets or raffle tickets at any time
during such occasion. Notes
